  "body": "**Precondition:** u should have a 1x1 chat opened with some user and several messages should be there (from sender and receiver). In case u dont have such a  chat - please create it.\r\n\r\n1. open 1x1 chat with several messages from both sender and receiver\r\n2. click the user profile picture and press block user button\r\n3. confirm the block action\r\n4. review messages\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1552\" alt=\"Screenshot 2021-09-08 at 12 39 01\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/132490810-8711b57c-a33e-4415-889a-547217b9cd6f.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/132490838-c93f4de1-eea5-47f2-984a-5c80086769fb.mov\r\n\r\n\r\nAs result, all messages sent from this user are not shown. NOTE: they will appear after the app is restarted. \r\n\r\n**Expected:** when blocking a user, u still should be able to see all messages in this chat.\r\n\r\n",
